  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to examine the correlation between UGT1A1 genotypes and the
      efficacy of CPT-11 based regimens (FOLFIRI, CPT-11+S-1, CPT-11) for patients with metastatic
      colorectal cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
